releases/0/tender/title: Construction contractors required for forthcoming project pipeline
releases/0/tender/description:
This early engagement is to understand the capability of the industry for forthcoming projects in the South East of England. Ideally companies will have DV vetted staff and or capability. The forthcoming projects include the following disciplines: Fencing, General Building, BMS Systems, Electrical works, Mechanical works, HVAC services and security services including CCTV.

Additional information: Please can you email your interest to partners@vfdefence.com with a general description of your companies capability and one of the team will come back to you.

releases/0/tender/title: Design support for forthcoming projects in the South East
releases/0/tender/description:
We are looking for Design companies who can support Design works from RIBA stage 0 to RIBA stage 4. Ideally companies will have DV cleared staff and be able to support our forthcoming pipeline of work across the following disciplines: Electrical, Mechanical, Security systems , BMS Systems and HVAC services.

Additional information: We would like to hear from suitably qualified companies by email. Please contact partners@vfdefence.com with your company contact details and a very brief summary of the services that you can provide and a member of the team will be in contact with you.
